A father was arrested earlier today for allegedly strangling his seven-year-old son to death at his Caneside home in Durban, the Phoenix Sun reports.It is alleged that the crime was sparked by a domestic violence issue between the husband and his wife.Unconfirmed reports have alleged that police officers found the father carrying the child s lifeless body on the road. He was subsequently arrested. Caxton News ServiceRead original story on phoenixsun.co.za